About this bootcamp
Python is a high-level, general-purpose programming language that is becoming popular in fields such as Data Science, Web Development, and IoT. Python is one of the top choices for Data Science because of its easy-to-use nature and the availability of a large number of powerful open-source libraries designed for solving Data Science problems.

In this bootcamp, you'll learn the basics of Python for Data Science. The Python functions and fundamentals covered in this bootcamp will introduce beginners to all the basics they will need to get started in Data Science.

At the end of this course, you will know the following things:

Installing Anaconda and introduction to Jupyter Notebook

Getting familiar with Python syntaxes and writing your first Python program

Variables, Data Types and Operators in Python

Data Structures and Data Types in Python

Python Functions and Packages
